<body>
    <h1>Manual Access Provisioning (Associate) (Use Case =E2=80=93 UC08)</h=
1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"ManualAccessProvisioning(Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93UC08)=
-ManualAccessProvisioningworkflow">Manual Access Provisioning workflow</h3>
<p>Table-23</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"d=
c71253b-cba2-472d-adad-2c44390780b3" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 314.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1485.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Manual Access Provisioning</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>This Manual Access Provisioning use case describes the process of how us=
ers can manage their access within SailPoint IdentityIQ. SailPoint Identity=
IQ will provision access privileges to target applications based on request=
.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the solution design docum=
ent.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>First Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Last Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Person Number</p></li>
<li>
<p>Assignment Status&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>System Worker Type&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Start Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Hire Date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective Date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Department&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Position&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Location&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Termination date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ministry&nbsp;</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Users for whom requests are raised should be present in the SailPoint Id=
entityIQ system with Active state. Access to be requested should be present=
 and requestable in SailPoint IdentityIQ.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>No automated trigger</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>User logged in to the SailPoint IdentityIQ</p></li>
<li>
<p>User requests for UKG elevated access, OCI or Oracle EPM Cloud.</p></li>
<li>
<p>The request will be reviewed for SOD violations. If violations exist, th=
e user will not be able to raise their request.</p></li>
<li>
<p>If no violations are found, the request is sent to the respective approv=
er(s).</p></li>
<li>
<p>If approved, application access is provisioned based on the request deta=
ils and email notification will be sent to the requestor, requestee, manage=
r and approver.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UKG/Kronos, Oracle EPM Cloud, OCI</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A user should request access in SailPoint IdentityIQ and SailPoint Ident=
ityIQ will provision the access/roles based on the request and approval dec=
isions.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A ServiceNow ticket will be created and assigned to the Ascension Health=
 Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>User Request</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
